articles.title: Biden says objects shot down over North America last week appear to not be part of China's spy balloon operation - CNN
articles.description: President Joe Biden on Thursday said that the United States has no indication that the three objects shot down in North American air space are tied to China's spy balloon program and are likely from private entities.
